data.description: Fully updated home sitting on 2 acres in the highly desired Sabine ISD. From the high cedar ceilings, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, the brick fire burning fire place, 4 large carpeted bedrooms and 3 large bathrooms, this beautiful home is guaranteed to have enough space for your family and friends. HVAC and roof recently replaced, along with new fencing put up around 1 acre, allowing endless possibilities with the other acre. This home comes with all the new appliances including the washer and dryer. Survey and recent appraisal on file for 370k! Buy into this home with equity from the start! You do not want to miss out on this deal!
